name: Carreducker at 50 Chocolate Studios
description:
A Victorian chocolate factory conversion with exposed girders, brickwork and Crittal-style windows. 

No 50 was transformed from a flat into a traditional, bespoke shoemaking workshop, showroom and shoe & leather craft training school.

name: The Ismaili Centre
description: Part of an international family of Ismaili Centres, a religious, cultural and social space for the Shia Ismaili Muslim community. The serenity of the entrance fountain to the roof garden reflects Muslim traditions in architecture and design
